    <item>
      <title>每一天都是生命中最独特的</title>
      <link>https://blog.liyaodong.com/posts/everyday-is-unique-day/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Aug 2014 09:17:06 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://blog.liyaodong.com/posts/everyday-is-unique-day/</guid>
      <description>&lt;amp-img&#xA;     src=&#34;https://image.liyaodong.com/uploads/2014/08/groundhog-day.jpg&#34;&#xA;     alt=&#34;groundhog-day &#34;&#xA;    &#xA;    sizes=&#34;(min-width: 720px) 700px, 100vw&#34;&#xA;    &#xA;         srcset=&#34;&#xA;        https://res.cloudinary.com/vanillad/image/fetch/w_450,q_auto,f_auto,c_scale,dpr_auto/https://image.liyaodong.com/uploads/2014/08/groundhog-day.jpg 450w,&#xA;        https://res.cloudinary.com/vanillad/image/fetch/w_750,q_auto,f_auto,c_scale,dpr_auto/https://image.liyaodong.com/uploads/2014/08/groundhog-day.jpg 750w,&#xA;        https://res.cloudinary.com/vanillad/image/fetch/w_900,q_auto,f_auto,c_scale,dpr_auto/https://image.liyaodong.com/uploads/2014/08/groundhog-day.jpg 900w,&#xA;        https://res.cloudinary.com/vanillad/image/fetch/w_1200,q_auto,f_auto,c_scale,dpr_auto/https://image.liyaodong.com/uploads/2014/08/groundhog-day.jpg 1200w,&#xA;        https://res.cloudinary.com/vanillad/image/fetch/w_1500,q_auto,f_auto,c_scale,dpr_auto/https://image.liyaodong.com/uploads/2014/08/groundhog-day.jpg 1500w,&#xA;        https://res.cloudinary.com/vanillad/image/fetch/q_auto,f_auto,c_scale,dpr_auto/https://image.liyaodong.com/uploads/2014/08/groundhog-day.jpg 2000w&#34;&#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;     width=&#34;700&#34;&#xA;     height=&#34;394&#34;&#xA;     layout=&#34;responsive&#34;&#xA;    on=&#34;tap: 526 &#34;&#xA;    role=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;    aria-label=&#34;Image lightbox button&#34;&#xA;   tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/amp-img&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;amp-image-lightbox&#xA;    id=&#34;526&#34;&#xA;    layout=&#34;nodisplay&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/amp-image-lightbox&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;昨晚看了一部电影《Groundhog Day》（土拨鼠之日），讲述了一个气象预报员重复过一天的生活，颇有感触写此博文。&lt;/p&gt;</description>
