    <item>
      <title>RGB色彩和CMYK色彩究竟有什么区别</title>
      <link>https://blog.liyaodong.com/posts/rgb-vs-cmyk/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Aug 2012 19:54:25 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://blog.liyaodong.com/posts/rgb-vs-cmyk/</guid>
      <description>&lt;amp-img&#xA;     src=&#34;https://image.liyaodong.com/uploads/2012/08/rgbcmyk.png&#34;&#xA;     alt=&#34;rgb &amp;amp; cmyk &#34;&#xA;    &#xA;    sizes=&#34;(min-width: 720px) 700px, 100vw&#34;&#xA;    &#xA;         srcset=&#34;&#xA;        https://res.cloudinary.com/vanillad/image/fetch/w_450,q_auto,f_auto,c_scale,dpr_auto/https://image.liyaodong.com/uploads/2012/08/rgbcmyk.png 450w,&#xA;        https://res.cloudinary.com/vanillad/image/fetch/w_750,q_auto,f_auto,c_scale,dpr_auto/https://image.liyaodong.com/uploads/2012/08/rgbcmyk.png 750w,&#xA;        https://res.cloudinary.com/vanillad/image/fetch/w_900,q_auto,f_auto,c_scale,dpr_auto/https://image.liyaodong.com/uploads/2012/08/rgbcmyk.png 900w,&#xA;        https://res.cloudinary.com/vanillad/image/fetch/w_1200,q_auto,f_auto,c_scale,dpr_auto/https://image.liyaodong.com/uploads/2012/08/rgbcmyk.png 1200w,&#xA;        https://res.cloudinary.com/vanillad/image/fetch/w_1500,q_auto,f_auto,c_scale,dpr_auto/https://image.liyaodong.com/uploads/2012/08/rgbcmyk.png 1500w,&#xA;        https://res.cloudinary.com/vanillad/image/fetch/q_auto,f_auto,c_scale,dpr_auto/https://image.liyaodong.com/uploads/2012/08/rgbcmyk.png 2000w&#34;&#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;     width=&#34;668&#34;&#xA;     height=&#34;328&#34;&#xA;     layout=&#34;responsive&#34;&#xA;    on=&#34;tap: 703 &#34;&#xA;    role=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;    aria-label=&#34;Image lightbox button&#34;&#xA;   tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/amp-img&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;amp-image-lightbox&#xA;    id=&#34;703&#34;&#xA;    layout=&#34;nodisplay&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/amp-image-lightbox&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;接触过设计的朋友应该会经常听到诸如RGB、CMYK之类的名词，但是对于很多设计新手往往不知道RGB与CMYK之间到底有什么区别和联系，甚至还经常询问如rgb转cmyk、cmyk和rgb的区别、打印用cmyk还是rgb、怎么转换成rgb这样的问题。&lt;/p&gt;</description>
